ets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個話攬炒 究竟咩叫攬炒呢？咩情況底下我地應該要攬炒呢？攬炒過後，會浴火重生，定係會萎靡不振呢？<br />\n呢排大家睇新聞都知道搞緊國安法，將香港變成一國一制啦，咁點解佢要做到呢一步要將香港嘅優勢剷除，因爲純粹憎班示威者？咁樣攬炒對佢有咩意義呢？咁講起「攬炒」喺我哋中文入面學過嘅中文入面就諗到<span style=\"color: red;\">藺相如</span>啦，佢連續兩次都係用自己嘅性命去脅迫秦國讓步，佢除咗有勇之外，都有好多策略喺入面。就係因爲佢知道自己唔會死，所以佢先夠膽去攬炒，咁佢嘅攬炒從何而嚟？<br />\n如果想知多啲 歡迎睇下條片 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EY_CcM_lW1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEY_CcM_lW1Q&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Es3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=24072128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EY_CcM_lW1Q</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林鄭柒婆話孟德拉話過：「教育嘅崩壞足以摧毀一個國家」，你睇啲藍絲黑警又唔做野又唔讀書就知啦。真正嘅孟德拉講過：「<span style=\"color: red;\">教育是你可以用來改變世界的最強大的武器</span>」。我相信，教育嘅力量勁過碾壓人民嘅坦克車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"快啲subscribe la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8c7005bc742772b8a67f7f90bf2915daf91133","tid":2051924,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"44cd3bc90e8ed4fa7972dc3b0d0d8834466e27fc","tid":2051924,"uid":226544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"7e98a6c027d646026d9944d3996406b93877d2a7","tid":2051924,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d98c3d2ea15ca22f78e387606ae584bb174a08","tid":2051924,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"