YlCmCIjJ4q2Dg&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Es3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=7a3bb939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQxGjJNcYuYlCmCIjJ4q2Dg</a><br />\n同埋有instagram page 希望大家可以 follow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/happy.chinesetutor?r=nametag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhappy.chinesetutor%3Fr%3Dnametag&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Es3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=4f8bdc03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/happy.chinesetutor?r=nametag</a><br />\n<br />\n我最新一堂係「藺相如的<span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span>哲學」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個話攬炒 究竟咩叫攬炒呢？咩情況底下我地應該要攬炒呢？攬炒過後，會浴火重生，定係會萎靡不振呢？<br />\n呢排大家睇新聞都知道搞緊國安法，將香港變成一國一制啦，咁點解佢要做到呢一步要將香港嘅優勢剷除，因爲純粹憎班示威者？咁樣攬炒對佢有咩意義呢？咁講起「攬炒」喺我哋中文入面學過嘅中文入面就諗到<span style=\"color: red;\">藺相如</span>啦，佢連續兩次都係用自己嘅性命去脅迫秦國讓步，佢除咗有勇之外，都有好多策略喺入面。就係因爲佢知道自己唔會死，所以佢先夠膽去攬炒，咁佢嘅攬炒從何而嚟？<br />\n如果想知多啲 歡迎睇下條片 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EY_CcM_lW1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEY_CcM_lW1Q&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Es3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=24072128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EY_CcM_lW1Q</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林鄭柒婆話孟德拉話過：「教育嘅崩壞足以摧毀一個國家」，你睇啲藍絲黑警又唔做野又唔讀書就知啦。真正嘅孟德拉講過：「<span style=\"color: red;\">教育是你可以用來改變世界的最強大的武器</span>」。我相信，教育嘅力量勁過碾壓人民嘅坦克車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我第一個po都有咁多人推就好了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"I mean 上一個 <img